These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, d&b, blues, soul
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, amber, turquise, black, emerald
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the fan of dubstep##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person who likes amber and the fan of soul##2
12. the person who likes black is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
13. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | hip-hop      | blues | soul   | dubstep    |
| Color   | black  | amber     | white | turquise | emerald  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

