.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, soy-milk, water, tea
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, r&b, techno
5 different games are played: poker, snooker, chess, backgammon, bridge
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person playing poker and the fan of techno##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person playing chess is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
11. the person playing chess is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage         | water | iced-tea | tea    | lemonade  | soy-milk    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b       | disco      | country | r&b        |
| Game   | bridge   | snooker     | poker    | backgammon  | chess     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

