.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, november, march, december, june
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, taxi, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Birthday   | june  | november | july | december | march        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Transport         | motorbike | scooter  | jet-ski    | airplane    | taxi        |

