.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, onion, papaya, tomato, watermelon
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, comedy, drama, western, romance
City: boston, colone, hamburg, prague, new-york
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person traveling to prague and the person eating tomato##2
 5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the british##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
12. the british is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | watermelon  | papaya     | tomato   | onion     | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | mystery    | drama  | western | comedy   |
