 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the chinese##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the canadian and the person playing chess##2
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the egyptian##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
