 7. the electrician is the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the police-officer is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the chef##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

