.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, nigerian, japanese, italian
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, golf, handball, sailing
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, yellow, coral, chestnut, brown
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who likes yellow and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the australian is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the brazilian##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 7. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes coral is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the japanese is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the nigerian is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality    | nigerian       | japanese    | italian | brazilian  | australian        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Color   | chestnut       | coral      | brown      | black | yellow  |

