.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There 5 different types of food: pear, lime, grapefruit, raspberry, pineapple
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people have 5 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, sudoku, filmmaking, collecting
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person eating raspberry is the fisherman##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is between the pilot and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person eating grapefruit##1
 8. the person eating pear is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
13. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Food      | pear      | lime         | raspberry      | grapefruit | pineapple     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | chess    | rock-climbing | sudoku    | collecting |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

