.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
There 5 different types of food: apple, nectarine, avocado, garlic, peach
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, aconite, azalea, bellflower, daisy
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is between the person eating apple and the person who growsiris##2
 6. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | card-games |
| Food   | apple   | garlic    | nectarine | peach | avocado      |
| Flower           | azalea | aconite    | iris       | bellflower     | daisy      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

