.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, cape-cod-climbing, skydiving
City: london, rome, edinburgh, new-york, nizza
House: wooden, victorian, palace, futuristic, cape-cod
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is between the malaysian and the cape-cod house##2
 3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person traveling to nizza is the wooden house##1
 5. the wooden house is between the thai and the palace house##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is the futuristic house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cape-cod-climbing is the victorian house##1
 9. the american is the victorian house##1
10. the person who's hobby is cape-cod-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | cape-cod-climbing |
| City   | rome    | nizza   | new-york | edinburgh | london   |
| House   | palace | wooden    | cape-cod    | futuristic       | victorian         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 